window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Level, conquer, build. </b></p> <p>Right as the world comes to an end, Devon is presented with an opportunity to escape Earth's demise. A most unusual benefactor grants him an opportunity at a new life in a land of magical cards, mythical creatures, and unique pedestals to manage his progress.</p> <p>Devon becomes a coveted dual mage, capable of harnessing the power of wind and ice. While he thinks his new abilities will make life easy, integration proves tough. He has a dentist as a sidekick, a land hydra as a pet, and brooding rage begging to be released. He'll battle dungeons, infestations, and monstrous beasts to claim his own slice of the land to call home. A place to become: the mayor of Mythos.</p>"; 
